            "title": "Largo appoints Gordon Babcock and Luis Rendón as co-COOs",
            "description": "<html><body><ul> <li>Largo (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LGO\" title=\"Largo Inc.\">LGO</a></span>) on Tuesday said it has appointed Gordon Babcock and Luis Rendón as Co-Chief Operating Officers, following the resignation of former COO, Celio Pereira for personal reasons.</li> <li>\"The Co-COO structure is intended to enhance oversight of the company’s operations, with each executive assuming responsibility for distinct operational areas to improve efficiencies,\" the company said.</li> <li>LGO  <font color=\"green\">+1.27%</font> after hours to  $1.7621.</li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20006033-largo-appoints-co-coos-to-strengthen-its-operational-leadership\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
