            "id": "4409758",
            "title": "TAV Havalimanlari Holding A.S. reports FY results",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>TAV Havalimanlari Holding A.S. <a href=\"https://ir.tav.aero/uploads/documents/Documents18022025183941_.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">press release</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TAVHY\" title=\"TAV Havalimanlari Holding A.S.\">OTCPK:TAVHY</a>): FY net income of €183 million.</li>\n<li>Revenue of €1.66 billion and EBITDA of €489 million.</li>\n<li>The company said it closed the year with a total of 107 million passengers, reflecting an 11% year-over-year growth, and served 71 million international passengers, marking a 13% increase over 2023.</li>\n<li>For 2025, the company anticipates EBITDA between €520–590 million and also expect to continue deleveraging, targeting a net debt/EBITDA ratio of 2.5–3.0x.</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
