            "id": "4409667",
            "title": "BrightSpire Q4 earnings drift down, as expected, as loan portfolio activity falls",
            "description": "<html><body><p>BrightSpire Capital (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BRSP\" title=\"BrightSpire Capital, Inc.\">BRSP</a></span>) on Tuesday delivered Q4 earnings that suffered from a slowdown in portfolio loan activity.</p> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20005791-brightspire-capital-inc-announces-fourth-quarter-and-full-year-2024-financial-results\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Q4 adjusted EPS\">Q4 adjusted EPS</a> of $0.18, matching the consensus, drifted down from $0.21 in the prior quarter.</p> <p>“The Company had a productive quarter and<span class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"> year highlighted by new loan originations and watchlist resolutions, all while continuing to maintain liquidity,\" said CEO Michael J. Mazzei. \"Looking ahead, we expect to continue to resolve watchlist and REO assets and grow the portfolio and earnings through new loan originations.”</span></p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">GAAP net book value retreated to $8.08 per share in Q4 from $8.39 in Q3, and undepreciated book value of $8.89 slid from $9.11 over the same period.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">At Dec. 31, 20924, the commercial real estate credit REIT's total loans portfolio stood at $2.52B with a total loan count of 76, down from $2.59B at Sept. 30, 2024.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Current expected credit loss reserve of $165.9M at the end of Q4 was up from $76.0M at the end of Q4 2023.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Conference <a href=\"https://www.brightspire.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"call\">call</a> on Feb. 19 at 10:00 a.m. ET.</p> </body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1393962755/image_1393962755.jpg",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4409667-brightspire-q4-earnings-drift-down-as-expected-as-loan-portfolio-activity-falls",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 01:03:44",
